# Kick Video Downloader - TDD Methodology

## 1. Project Context
- Download Kick streams automatically
- Store in organized structure
- Serve via nginx web interface

## 2. TDD Rules
- Tests first, code later
- Each feature: test → implement → refactor
- No automation without validation

## 3. Architecture
- src/downloader.py - Main download logic
- src/server.py - API endpoints  
- tests/test_downloader.py - Download tests
- deploy/ - nginx, systemd configs

## 4. Quality Gates
- All downloads must be validated
- File integrity checks
- Error handling for network issues